I didn’t mind this puzzle but I could see the storm coming. The theme and execution was just too obscure and unrewarding for many. To be honest if I had come up with this theme and had to stretch this far to execute it, I would have rejected it in my mind before submitting it (and am surprised that the editors didn’t). Again, to be clear, I found it engaging and solvable personally and applaud the constructors for their perseverance and technical prowess, but I’m not surprised that many did not and feel that the negative reviews are not unwarranted.

