The revealer has two parts.  First, figuring out the word that "Renounced" is referring to.  Second, figuring out a word that sounds like either FOR or GONE. Four seems the most likely candidate.  So do any of the theme answers make sense if they originally had the number four?  No.  So where is the four?  Oh, each answer has four of the same letters, and when you remove them, i.e. make them "GONE", then the theme answers make sense.  Not saying it was easy, but Thursday trickery often isn't.

